Collaborative Filtering - The most popular techniques for building recommender systems

Nguyen Minh Thanh (thanhleo92@gmail.com)

30 October 2017

1 Gii thiu

C nhng hin tng m chng ta gp rt nhiu ln nh :

  • Youtube gi nhng video m bn c th s thch

  • Facebook gi kt bn

  • Sau khi mua hng trn Amazon, h thng s t ng gi ra cc mn hng Frequently bought together

  • Netflix gi phim cho ngi dng

Bng cch qung co sn phm hng vo tng i tng nh vy, hiu qu ca vic Marketing s tng ln cng nh tng hiu qu kinh doanh. Thut ton ng ng sau nhng ng dng ny l nhng thut ton Machine Learning c tn gi l Recommendation Systems hoc Recommender Systems

Recommendation Systems c tui i kh tr so vi cc thut ton Machine Learning khc v n xut hin t nhu cu bng n ca Internet cch y 10-15 nm trc.

2 Hai nhm chnh ca Recommendation Systems

C 2 thc th chnh ca Recommendation Systems l \(Items\) v \(Users\). Trong \(Users\) l ngi dng, cn \(Items\) l sn phm: b phim, bi ht, sch Mc ch chnh ca cc Recommendation Systems l d bo mc quan tm ca mt User ti Item no a ra chin lc Recommend ph hp

Cc Recommendation Systems thng c chia thnh 2 nhm ln:

  • Content-based systems: h thng s recommend da trn c tnh ca Item. VD: mt User xem rt nhiu video trn Youtube th loi nhc tr Vit ca Sn Tng th h thng Recommendation Systems s gi cho Users ny mt s video cng th loi nh Lc Tri. Cch tip cn ny yu cu vic sp xp cc Item vo cc nhm r rng, tuy nhin nu Item khng c nhm c th hoc kh xc nh nhm th vic s dng Content-based Systems l khng th

  • Collaborative Filtering: l h thng gi item da trn s tng quan gia cc Users v Items. C th hiu rng mt Item c recommend cho mt User s da trn nhng Users c hnh ng tng t. VD: A,T,N u thch xem clip AOE ca GAMETV, ngoi ra T v A thch xem clip ca Chim S i Nng. Da trn thng tin ca T v A, h thng c th d on rng N s thch xem clip ca Chim S i Nng v gi cho ngi dng ny

\(Bi vit ny chng ta s i vo nghin cu Collaborative Filtering do c tnh ng dng cao trong thc t\)

3 Collaborative Filtering

3.1 Hai nhm ca Collaborative Filtering

Collaborative Filtering c chia thnh 2 nhm :

  • User-based CF: CF gi User A s dng Item da trn nhng Users c hnh ng tng t nh A (nh VD nu trn)

  • Item-based CF: CF gi User A s dng Item da trn nhng Item m User khc tng s dng. VD: User va xem xong phn I tp phim Game of Thrones, Netfix s gi ngi dng xem tip phn II ca b phim ny

3.2 Cc bc tnh ton Items Based Collaborative Filtering

VD: Xy dng CF cho khch hng da trn d liu lch s vote cho cc b phim

Cc b phim s c khch hng nh gi trn thang im t 1 n 5

  • Bc 1: Xy dng ma trn rating matrix da trn mc nh gi cc b phim ca cc khch hng ny

  • Bc 2: Normalise d liu rating: Vic u tin CF s tnh trung bnh cc rating ca tng User, sau s tnh gi tr gia cc cc rating n cc gi tr trung bnh ny. Bn cht ca vic normalise d liu n t vic tnh cch ca khch hng lun khc nhau (c nhng ngi khi xem b phim thy rt hay s nh gi 5, tuy nhin c nhng ngi kh tnh hn ch nh gi 4). Do vy, khi tnh ton trung bnh s mang li mc nh gi l tt nht khi nhng gi tr ln hn trung bnh l b phim khch hng thch cn di trung bnh l khng thch.

  • Bc 3: Tnh ton Similarities gia cc Users v Items : Phng php thng c s dng l Cosine Similarity gia cc Users vi nhau. Gi tr ca Cosin Similarity gia cc Users s trong khong [-1,1]. Gi tr 1 th hin 2 vector hon ton Similarity vi nhau, vi - 1 s th hin ngc li qua s to ra ma trn Similarity. T ma trn Similarity ta s bit nhng Users no c hnh vi ging vi Users no.

  • Bc 4: S dng phng php K-nearest neighbor d bo gi tr rating b missing. CF s la chn k Users c mc similarity cao nht (tc cc khch hng c hnh vi ging nht)

  • Bc 5: Tnh gi tr d bo rating items da trn trung bnh iu ha gi tr similarity v rating ca cc k users ging n nht

4 S khc nhau gia CF v Association Rule

  • Data

    Data ca thut ton Association rule lch s giao dch ca khch hng, tc khch hng c giao dch trn sn phm hay khng.

    Data ca CF s da trn lch s giao dch khch hng tuy nhin c phn chia thuc tnh thch hay khng thch sn phm

  • S lng recommend

    Association rule s recommend da trn rule c lift ln hn 1 do vy khng phi khch hng no cng c recommend s dng sn phm

    CF s recommend cho tt c cc khch hng v thut ton c gng in y ch s recommend cho cc sn phm ca tng khch hng

5 Thc hnh:

  • R cung cp package Recommenderlab phc v cho vic x l Collaborative Filtering, tuy nhin package ny c mt vi nhc im nh:

S dng matrix dng \(Realratingmatrix\) rt tn dung lng RAM

Vic tnh ton rt phc tp v nng. Gi s c 500.000 khch hng, vic tnh ton Cosine Similarity gia tng cp khch hng vi nhau s to ra 120 triu gi tr. Vic ny khin cho my tnh khng th tnh ton ni

  • Do vy chung ta s s dng phng php khc trong R bng vic s dng Sparse Matrix - Cch lu tr d liu gip gim nh vic tnh ton.

  • Bi vit ny s s dng data lch s s dng th tn dng ca khch hng trn cc Category qua s recommend cc Category ph hp vi khch hnh phc v vic upsell campaign. Collaborative Filtering s c xy dng da trn lch s giao dch th tn dng t 30/7/2017 tr v trc v s c test trn khong thi gian tng lai n thi im 31/10/2017 nh gi xem vi vic ta cha c nhng tc ng n khch hng th hnh vi ca khch hng c thay i ging vi d bo l chnh xc bao nhiu

5.2 Tnh recommendation cho khch hng s dng sn phm

ratings_matrix <- Matrix(as.matrix(score_credit_card_long %>% select(-1)), sparse = TRUE) 

items_to_predict <- 1:ncol(ratings_matrix)
users <- 1:nrow(ratings_matrix)
prediction_indices <- as.matrix(expand.grid(users,items_to_predict))
recommender_result <- predict_cf(ratings_matrix, 
                                 prediction_indices, 
                                 alg_method = "ibcf", 
                                 normalization = TRUE, 
                                 similarity_metric = cal_cos, 
                                 k = 300, 
                                 make_positive_similarities = FALSE, 
                                 rowchunk_size = 2000, 
                                 columnchunk_size = 1000)

recommender_result_final <- as.data.frame(as.matrix(recommender_result)) 
recommender_result_final$target_id <- score_credit_card_long$target_id
recommender_result_final <- recommender_result_final %>% 
  melt(id.vars = "target_id")

recommend_data <- left_join(recommender_result_final,
                       score_credit_card_long %>% melt(id.vars = "target_id"),
                       by = c("target_id", "variable"))

recommend <- recommend_data %>% 
  filter(value.y == 0) %>%
  group_by(target_id) %>% 
  arrange(desc(value.x)) %>% 
  slice(1:3) %>% 
  as.data.frame()

Kt qu ca CF s l 3 sn phm c ch s recommendation cao nht s c la chn th recommend cho khch hng
